            <formatted-text>
              <run bold='true'>• Research &amp; Development department records the highest employee attrition.</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true'>• Employees working overtime demonstrate significantly higher turnover trends.</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true'>• Attrition is more common among employees with fewer years at company.</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
              <run bold='true'>• Workforce retention improves with higher employee experience and satisfaction.</run>
            </formatted-text>
